OL,3,CGrieving family join campaign for
OL,4,Crestrictions on young drivers after
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FA family from Rhondda Cynon Taff whose
OL,8,Fson died in a fatal crash have joined
OL,9,Fcalls for restrictions on young
OL,10,Fdrivers.
OL,12,FCallum Griffiths, 19 from Porth, was
OL,13,Fone of three killed in a traffic
OL,14,Fcollision last December in Coedely.
OL,16,FHis family are now calling for
OL,17,FGraduated Driving Licenses, that would
OL,18,Fmean introducing restrictions on
OL,19,Fdrivers under 25.
