OL,7,F"I think anything we can do to not
OL,8,Fjust save young lives, but ultimately
OL,9,Fto stop the ripple effect that has
OL,10,Fhappened to us," Callum's mum, Natalie
OL,11,FGriffiths, told the Y Byd ar Bedwar
OL,12,Fprogramme.
OL,14,F"Our children are being forgotten and
OL,15,Fwe as parents are never going to let
OL,16,Fthat happen", she added.
OL,18,FThe new restrictions could include a
OL,19,Fban on carrying passengers under the
OL,20,Fage of 25 and restrictions on driving
OL,21,Fat night.
