OL,7,FSimilar restrictions are in place in
OL,8,Fcountries like New Zealand and Canada
OL,9,Fand have been seen as a successful way
OL,10,Fto limit the number of car accidents
OL,11,Famongst young people.
OL,13,FMs Griffiths, who is now a member of
OL,14,Fthe Bereaved Families campaign group,
OL,15,Fcontinued: "These licences could make
OL,16,Fyoung people think before making
OL,17,Fdecisions, give more awareness and
OL,18,Fmore experience behind the wheel."
