OL,7,FTalking about how her son paid the
OL,8,Fultimate price in losing his life, Ms
OL,9,FGriffiths added: "Callum has had the
OL,10,Fgreatest restriction there could
OL,11,Fpossibly be.
OL,13,F"If the Government were able to listen
OL,14,Fto the wider voices, perhaps with
OL,15,Fexemptions in place for certain
OL,16,Fsituations, it would just afford young
OL,17,Fpeople greater freedom in time."
OL,19,FCallum Griffiths was a world champion
OL,20,Fkickboxer, a talented barber and a
OL,21,Fsociable and popular boy.
