OL,7,FAccording to his mother, he was "a
OL,8,Fgood boy with a smile that lit up a
OL,9,Froom."
OL,11,F"We can't make new memories with
OL,12,FCallum, and that's really hard."
OL,14,FA fund in memory of Callum has raised
OL,15,Fover #11,000 for charity 2Wish Cymru,
OL,16,Fan organisation that has "saved" his
OL,17,Ffamily and friends in their grief.
OL,19,F"It's been a struggle and it's never
OL,20,Fgoing to get better," said Shane
OL,21,FWilliams, Callum's best friend.
