OL,7,F"We see pictures of him on our phones
OL,8,Fall the time, but to know he's always
OL,9,Fthere is quite comforting.
OL,11,F"He was the funniest guy I've ever
OL,12,Fmet. We'll all miss him terribly,"
OL,13,Fechoed friend Daniel Reeves.
OL,15,FCallum was a passenger when the car he
OL,16,Fwas travelling in collided with a bus.
OL,17,FJesse Owen and Morgan Smith also died
OL,18,Fin the crash.
