OL,7,F"Never did I ever contemplate that
OL,8,FCallum wouldn't be coming home that
OL,9,Fnight," said Ms Griffiths.
OL,11,F"I just kept praying really, and
OL,12,Fhoping that if Cal was there, that he
OL,13,Fwas okay, that he would be, you know,
OL,14,Fsafe."
OL,16,F"I don't think as a family we'll ever
OL,17,Freally accept it or understand why
OL,18,FCallum and his friends were taken. It
OL,19,Fwas just a horrific, horrific period."
