OL,7,FAccording to the Welsh Government,
OL,8,Fthere is evidence that licences like
OL,9,Fthis can reduce accidents among young
OL,10,Fpeople but that this area is not
OL,11,Fdevolved to Wales.
OL,13,FY Byd ar Bedwar understands that the
OL,14,FDepartment for Transport has
OL,15,Fcommissioned research to support new
OL,16,Fdrivers in the past but in response to
OL,17,Fthe latest campaign, it said that it
OL,18,Fwas too early for the new government
OL,19,Fto comment on the matter.
